{
  "stem": "4189.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, they supervised the work that we had to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we built this camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We put it up very fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We put up tents, huge tents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for sleeping beds-- beds?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were bunks, like.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to build three levels or four levels of, of a structure like where five people used to sleep, one next to the other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it was so crowded in there that we had to sleep one way one head one way, and then the next person had to sleep on the opposite with their head to the feet of the other guy so that we could fit five people in there.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were no sanitary conditions, no toilets or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to dig ditches and put-- chop trees off and take off all the branches and put the tree over the ditch.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was our toilet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very bad condition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What we had to do there, we had to build a road that goes to, to the ocean, to the water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, Boulogne, Calais is opposite of the English Channel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On a clear day, we could see the cliffs of Dover.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, this is the shortest distance between Dover and Calais.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's the shortest distance on the, on the North Sea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Nazis thought that if the Allies would invade Europe, they would come from that side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they built very heavy fortification up there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They built what they called an Atlantic Wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The wall was-- they built-- they actually built a wall that was as thick as a whole house, solid concrete reinforced with steel, heavy bunkers all around.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole beach was all barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And inside the water, the ocean, going into the ocean, was all mined.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
